#HELPS

-1 SUMMARY~
To access any files on this list, type 'help <name>'.  If you know of any
helpfiles that are missing or in need of updating, leave a note on the
personal board to an immortal, as appropriate.

 License Files -	Diku, Merc, Godwars, Godwars-history, Godwars-info.
 Important Files -	Newbie, Rules, Disclaimer ...
 Class Files - 		Class, Clan, Reqs, Leaders.
 Miscellaneous Files -	Stats, Stances, Styles, Experience.
 PK Files -		Pk, Death, Decapitate, Escape, Status, ...
~

-1 NEWBIE~
#7#b#uPlease read this before playing.#n
Welcome to Godwars, a modified Godwars Deluxe codebase.  A few things for
new players to note.

* Read #Rhelp rules#n.  Ignorance is not an excuse.
* Take a look at #Ghelp class#n and #Ghelp clan#n.
* Read the #Cnote boards#n — you will find useful information there.  In
 particular, check the #Cannounce board#n for important announcements.
* Please read #Lhelp reqs#n for classing requirements.
* Characters inactive for extended periods may be subject to deletion.
* Refer to #Phelp stats#n for information on your character's attributes.
* You may want to look into #yhelp dirs#n for directions to good exp areas.

#7#b#u* Immortal positions are not freely available and have requirements.#n
~
 
